name: CARBON BLACK APP CONTROL [<%= eventname %>]
description: Carbon Black App Control alerts for threats with low severity.
query: class=carbonblack_er product:`app control` has:dsthost severity:[2, 3] NOT srcipv4:$exclusions.global.srcipv4

name: CARBON BLACK APP CONTROL [<%= eventname %>]
description: Carbon Black App Control alerts for threats with medium severity.
query: class=carbonblack_er product:`app control` has:dsthost severity:[4, 5] NOT srcipv4:$exclusions.global.srcipv4

name: CARBON BLACK APP CONTROL [<%= eventname %>]
description: Carbon Black App Control alerts for threats with high severity.
query: class=carbonblack_er product:`app control` has:dsthost severity:[6, 7] NOT srcipv4:$exclusions.global.srcipv4

name: CARBON BLACK APP CONTROL [<%= eventname %>]
description: Carbon Black App Control alerts for threats with critical severity.
query: class=carbonblack_er product:`app control` has:dsthost severity:[8, 9] NOT srcipv4:$exclusions.global.srcipv4
